<paragraph blockId="65.[151,578,800,828]" box="[151,578,800,828]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,578,800,828]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="65" pageNumber="66" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,578,800,828]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66">
Genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Peringuey, 1900" authorityName="Peringuey" authorityYear="1900" box="[238,578,800,828]" class="Insecta" family="Cetoniidae" genus="Placodidus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="65" pageNumber="66" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[238,372,801,828]" italics="true" pageId="65" pageNumber="66">Placodidus</emphasis>
Péringuey, 1900
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="65.[151,1437,873,972]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66">
The genus was revised by 
<bibRefCitation author="Krikken, J." box="[442,614,873,900]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66" pagination="367 - 380" refId="ref84932" refString="Krikken, J. (1976) Taxonomy of the african genus Placodidus (Coleoptera: Cetoniidae). Proceedings of the Koninklijke Nederlandse Akademie van Wetenschappen, Series C Biological and Medical Sciences, 79 (4), 367 - 380." type="journal article" year="1976">Krikken (1976)</bibRefCitation>
which recognized six species. Later, 
<bibRefCitation author="Krikken, J." box="[1027,1213,873,900]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66" pagination="57 - 60" refId="ref85011" refString="Krikken, J. (1979 b) A new Placodidus from Angola (Coleoptera: Cetoniidae). Journal of the Entomological Society of South Africa, 42 (1), 57 - 60." type="journal article" year="1979">Krikken (1979b)</bibRefCitation>
described one more species. The species are myrmecophylous, presenting a very flat body conformation adapted to this habit. There are two species recorded for 
<collectingCountry box="[431,513,945,971]" name="Angola" pageId="65" pageNumber="66">Angola</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Krikken, J." box="[528,688,945,971]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66" pagination="367 - 380" refId="ref84932" refString="Krikken, J. (1976) Taxonomy of the african genus Placodidus (Coleoptera: Cetoniidae). Proceedings of the Koninklijke Nederlandse Akademie van Wetenschappen, Series C Biological and Medical Sciences, 79 (4), 367 - 380." type="journal article" year="1976">Krikken 1976</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Krikken, J." box="[699,773,945,972]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66" pagination="57 - 60" refId="ref85011" refString="Krikken, J. (1979 b) A new Placodidus from Angola (Coleoptera: Cetoniidae). Journal of the Entomological Society of South Africa, 42 (1), 57 - 60." type="journal article" year="1979">1979b</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
